                >
                <h4 class="font-medium text-sm leading-none mt-1">
                  Hello World! ðŸ‘‹
                </h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                  Wrote my first line of code
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <Card title="Recent Certifications" class="md:col-span-1">
        <svg
          slot="icon"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="16"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-muted-foreground"
          ><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle><polyline
            points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"></polyline></svg
        >
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm">
            <a
              href="https://www.credly.com/badges/de4b2160-0dd5-4ef0-9c2d-f880cbbc813e/public_url"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="flex items-center justify-between text-[12px] gap-11 hover:text-primary ease-in-out duration-300"
            >
              <span class="font-medium">AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">2025</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
      <Card title="Recommendations" class="md:col-span-2">
        <svg
          slot="icon"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="16"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-muted-foreground"
          ><path
            d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"
          ></path><path
            d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"
          ></path></svg
        >
        <blockquote
          class="italic text-muted-foreground text-sm border-l-2 border-primary/50 pl-4 py-1"
        >
          "Edric was an excellent student to work with. He consistently arrived
          on time, learned quickly, and contributed well in group settings. His
          professionalism and positive attitude made working with him a genuine
